    "1302708": {
        "Desc": "Find where Apep is hidden",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Looks like we've been sent back out... Still in one piece, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "The dragon will need to rest for a very long time before it is fully healthy again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "It's not as ruthless as it was before. Curing the dragon of its illness has seemingly made it more open to reason."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Nobody's in a good mood when they're feeling sick!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Even though we accomplished something really important, Paimon still doesn't feel happy for some reason."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Bringing everyone home was supposed to be a happy occasion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But it seems to have lost some of its meaning."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Indeed, although they'll still have the chance to be born again, they've lost their memories of their journey and their feelings for their homeland."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Each opportunity for growth is unique in its own way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Perhaps the immense power we released was the pouring out of all these irreplaceable emotions that had built up over time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Can you really call a place with no family your home...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Family... Right! The Hydro Fungus left behind its family."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Those two Fungi might be waiting for it to return."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, yeah! Let's hurry and go take a look. How are we going to explain all the complicated things that happened...?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1302709": {
        "Desc": "Head to the Heart of Oasis",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "They're still here! Have they really been waiting here all this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "We're back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "♪~"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I'm sorry, I really am... But it's gone home and won't be able to return for a very long time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "!!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Don't be sad. It did it to protect you. Your happiness is more important to it than anything else in the world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "It said that \"Nur\" is its most important family member."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "That's your name, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "N... Nur..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "This is wonderful... So it has left traces of itself after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "They will definitely meet again, someday."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1302710": {
        "Desc": "Confirm the situation at your current location",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So that elemental life-form came all the way here on its own and spent a long time by itself?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wouldn't it already have become The Withering like the others...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "There is a chance that it could avoid that end, using the power of something here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I'm referring to what was used to fight against the Abyss. It once repaired the rifts of Teyvat long ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "It has the ability to purify and stabilize powers that shouldn't exist in Teyvat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Forbidden knowledge that its light has shone upon is kept here forever in a different form..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You mean... the Oozing Filth?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Yup. It's just like soap bubbles that rise to the water's surface."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, another strange metaphor... But Paimon somehow gets this one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Elemental Being: Floating Hydro Fungus",
                    "T": "What the Lord of Dendro means is that the apocalypse was altered by the power of the giant spike and hidden within the Oozing Filth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Yes, and it shouldn't be far from here. Let's go and take a look."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
